libfvad — voice activity detection library extracted from the WebRTC
project (https://github.com/dpirch/libfvad), vendored unchanged from the
copy embedded in the arf-recog-adaptive-vad UniMRCP plugin
(plugins/arf-recog-adaptive-vad/src/libfvad/).

